function.name: abs.Expression
function.arg:
<%@ livebos language='javascript' %>
var fhbz = ABS_SQLVALUE("select paramvalue from jgcrm.tsysparam  where paramname='ams.system'");
var fhz=true;
if(fhbz==0){
  fhz=true;
}else{
  var bean = ABS_LOADBEAN("com.apex.bss.mod.ibb.systemdocking.apexsoft.livebosbean.TaskEndBean");
  var result = bean.perform($Login.User.UserID,O_WORKFLOW.InstID);
  var code = result.get('O_CODE');
  var note = result.get('O_NOTE');
  if(code > 0){
      ABS_SETRETNOTE(note);
     fhz= true;
   }else{
      ABS_SETRETNOTE(note);
      fhz= false;
   }
}
fhz;

dynOwner.expression:
["instr(',' ||
 (select owner
 from (select owner
 from jgcrm.os_historystep
 where step_id = 32
 and action_id = 33
 and entry_id = (select instid
 from ecif.lcIB_FKYJHFB
 where id = {0})
 order by finish_date asc)
 where rownum = 1) || ',',
 ',' || id || ',') > 0 or instr(',' ||
 (select owner
 from (select owner
 from jgcrm.os_historystep
 where step_id = 32
 and action_id <0
 and entry_id = (select instid
 from ecif.lcIB_FKYJHFB
 where id = {0})
 order by finish_date asc)
 where rownum = 1) || ',',
 ',' || id || ',') > 0 ",[{"expression":"O_WORKFLOW.ID","length":0,"scale":0,"type":0}]]
